title: Team Immunity is looking for a mid-laner
body:
Hi guys, we're team Immunity and we're searching for a mid-laner for 5v5 rankeds.

Requirements :

* Has to be active daily at least 6-10 PM CET during the week and should have even more time in the weekends
* Age: 16+
* Plat/diamond elo in soloQ
* Around Gold elo in flex
* Can communicate and speak english fluently
* Can adapt pretty fast to any playstyle (+has a large champion pool)

See you on the rift{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}

replies.body: Will accept your invite after i finished my current Game!
